& [ExplicitWindowExpansion] is a project-local finite diagnostic contract
  + [source_snapshot_uuid] is 9803f94c-e2c1-423a-bede-f1c4a56cc89f
  + [canonical_specification_uuid] is 55cf5b4b-f50b-4627-9315-5d2f5d56f114
