& [ExplicitWindowExpansionSJS] is the specification justification trace
  + [processed_stage_set] is source_preserved, delineated, canonicalized, constraint_checked, justified, and implementation_scoped
  + [processing_result] is accepted_bounded_diagnostic_expansion
  + [reasoning_result] is larger zero counts and additional smoothing policies can test whether previous sharp/Fejer residual behavior was local window choice, cutoff sensitivity, or a broader truncation phenomenon

